{"tid":1238260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰咪扮無知, 612實關你事! 搵下屬做擋箭牌, 瀨埋醫管真無恥!","createTime":"2019-06-17T17:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T14:46:36.000Z","uid":258927,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83062dd846bee539d9bd9cb15c419a204e70200a","tid":1238260,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:57:37.000Z","msg":"盧偉聰咪扮無知, 6.12實關你事!<br />\n搵下屬做擋箭牌, 瀨埋醫管真無恥!<br />\n<br />\n一百五十催淚彈, 記者前鋒齊硬撐.<br />\n黑警廿發布袋彈, 擺到明係殺人犯!<br />\n仲有血腥橡膠彈, 差啲射盲人隻眼!<br />\n呢啲叫最低武力, 不如搵日請你食?<br />\n<br />\n速龍失控需嚴懲, 黑警交出委任證!<br />\n和平集會好理性, 誣衊暴動絕不認!<br />\n釋放無辜示威者, 追究責任無得傾!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6月20號, 政府必須作出正面回應!<br />\n否則, 6月21號立法會開會, 一齊開佢老母!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n#生於亂世有種責任<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#求share出fb/ig/tg/wtsapp</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/588784021102919701/590181272962203668/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F588784021102919701%2F590181272962203668%2Funknown.png&h=23a60374&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21aa4709fd824cfc4bcaa2f199d2c0fc1b882feb","tid":1238260,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:57:51.000Z","msg":"6月20號, 政府必須作出正面回應!<br />\n否則, 6月21號立法會開會, 一齊開佢老母!<br />\n<br />\n#生於亂世有種責任<br />\n#求share出fb/ig/tg/wtsapp"},{"pid":"9c36b94ed88108b08e215070162d2ddae0b1d762","tid":1238260,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:58:04.000Z","msg":"6月20號, 政府必須作出正面回應!<br />\n否則, 6月21號立法會開會, 一齊開佢老母!<br />\n<br />\n#生於亂世有種責任<br />\n#求share出fb/ig/tg/wtsapp"},{"pid":"f650063d9c6bd0dedb87156d3b3668a825e45c62","tid":1238260,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:58:16.000Z","msg":"6月20號, 政府必須作出正面回應!<br />\n否則, 6月21號立法會開會, 一齊開佢老母!<br />\n<br />\n#生於亂世有種責任<br />\n#求share出fb/ig/tg/wtsapp"},{"pid":"2d5dc47ea25e1b4bf88b80b9a533a0dd6